#: ../../source/examples/Example_07_跨品种套利.md:1
msgid "跨品种套利交易策略（教学等价版）"
msgstr ""
"Cross-product arbitrage trading strategies (educational equivalent "
"version)"

#: ../../source/examples/Example_07_跨品种套利.md:3
msgid ""
"参考来源：`docs/_joinquant_migration_source/Example_07_跨品种套"
"利.ipynb` 第一个 Markdown cell。   说明：原 notebook 已标注“信息有问题"
"需要更正”，本示例以 qteasy 可稳定复现的教学实现为准。"
msgstr ""
"Reference source: `docs/_joinquant_migration_source/Example_07_跨商品套"
"利.ipynb` First Markdown cell. Note: The original notebook was marked "
"\"Information issues require correction\". This example is based on "
"the reproducible implementation in qteasy."

#: ../../source/examples/Example_07_跨品种套利.md:6
msgid "策略思路"
msgstr "Strategy and Ideas"

#: ../../source/examples/Example_07_跨品种套利.md:8
msgid "选取两个高相关交易标的，构造价差 `spread = p1 - p2`；"
msgstr ""
"Select two highly correlated trading instruments and construct a price "
"spread `spread = p1 - p2`;"

#: ../../source/examples/Example_07_跨品种套利.md:9
msgid "在滚动窗口内计算价差均值与标准差，得到 zscore；"
msgstr ""
"The mean and standard deviation of the price difference are calculated "
"within a scrolling window to obtain the zscore."

#: ../../source/examples/Example_07_跨品种套利.md:10
msgid ""
"当 zscore 高于上阈值时做空价差（卖出第一个、买入第二个），低于下阈值时"
"做多价差；"
msgstr ""
"When zscore is above the upper threshold, short spreads are opened "
"(sell the first one and buy the second one); when zscore is below the "
"lower threshold, long spreads are opened."

#: ../../source/examples/Example_07_跨品种套利.md:11
msgid "回归到退出阈值附近时平仓。"
msgstr ""
"Close the position when the price returns to near the exit threshold."

#: ../../source/examples/Example_07_跨品种套利.md:13
msgid "qteasy 实现说明"
msgstr "QtEasy Implementation Instructions"

#: ../../source/examples/Example_07_跨品种套利.md:15
msgid "本文使用 `PT` 信号，策略类为 `Example07CrossSymbolSpread`；"
msgstr ""
"This article uses the `PT` signal and the strategy class is "
"`Example07CrossSymbolSpread`;"

#: ../../source/examples/Example_07_跨品种套利.md:16
msgid ""
"为降低数据依赖，示例脚本默认使用日频指数对（教学近似），不是原始分钟期"
"货合约对；"
msgstr ""
"To reduce data dependency, the example script uses daily index pairs "
"(approximate for teaching purposes) by default, instead of the "
"original minute futures contract pairs;"

#: ../../source/examples/Example_07_跨品种套利.md:17
msgid ""
"若你本地具备期货分钟数据，可将脚本中的 `asset_type/asset_pool/freq` 替"
"换为期货版本。"
msgstr ""
"If you have local futures minute data, you can replace `asset_type/"
"asset_pool/freq` in the script with the futures version."

#: ../../source/examples/Example_07_跨品种套利.md:43
msgid "可执行脚本"
msgstr "Executable script"

#: ../../source/examples/Example_07_跨品种套利.md:45
msgid "`examples/strategy_example_07.py`"
msgstr "`examples/strategy_example_07.py`"
